since a Dutton founded the town.

51
00:05:04.771 --> 00:05:07.263
As it stands. the
defendant is correct.

52
00:05:07.340 --> 00:05:09.935
Our land use laws
are quite clear.

53
00:05:10.010 --> 00:05:11.774
For this commission to
grant eminent domain.

54
00:05:11.845 --> 00:05:15.577
you must show
public need. not desire.

55
00:05:15.682 --> 00:05:18.447
I think that's enough
posturing. Let's put it to a vote.

56
00:05:18.518 --> 00:05:21.317
The plaintiff hasn't shown
any legal imperative for a vote.

57
00:05:21.388 --> 00:05:22.617
No. this case is dismissed.

58
00:05:22.856 --> 00:05:24.051
